Titolo: Quest for the Code

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: STARBRIGHT Asthma CD-ROM Game: Quest for the Code is an  interactive asthma adventure game developed by Starbright. The game is available in both English and Spanish and free to both children with asthma and their carers. The game was designed for educational purposes.Originally developed as a CD-ROM game for use in schools, it was later made available online for free for use by parents, teachers, and students.It was part of a series including Starbright Diabetes CD-Rom, Starbright Explorer Series, and Starbright Hospital Pals.

Genere: Non specificato


